premise_source_doc_sentence: The Kuala Lumpur -- Kuala Selangor Expressway  (  Lebuhraya Kuala Lumpur -- Kuala Selangor  )  , KLS  (  formerly Ijok-Templer Park Highway  (  Lebuhraya Ijok-Taman Templer  )  , LATAR  )  or sometimes called LATAR Expressway  (  Lebuhraya LATAR  )  , E25 , is an expressway in Selangor , Malaysia .
